text: Unmukt Chand (born 26 March 1993) is an Indian cricketer. He is a right-hand batsman who usually opens the batting. Chand took his India Under-19 cricket team team to the U-19 Cricket World Cup victory in 2012. He scored an 111 not out in the final against Australia in Townsville,India U-19 wins World Cup under the captaincy of Unmukt Chand and got the praise of Australian great batsman Ian Chappell. == References == Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:People from New Delhi
